title: HF_018_APFBW.zip
description:
This is the first hotfix for V1.15. No earlier hotfixes is needed.

These files aim to fix/add:
Missing Energy Circle
No Retard Callout when thrust levers at ldle
A321 Lower ECAM FCTL Spoilers numbering.
Tweaks to FBW auto trim
Unzip the contents of FSXMainFolder in the attached file to the main FSX folder, overwriting all existing files. This hotfix 018 is intended to be inserted on top of version 1.15.
